-- BBVA plans early redemption of 4.245 bln euros of mortgage-backed bonds
-- 
-- Wed Jun 18, 2014 07:11AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, June 18 (Reuters) - Spanish bank BBVA <BBVA.MC> said on Wednesday that it plans to redeem early a total of 4.245 billion euros ($5.75 billion) of mortgage-backed bonds issued in 2011 and 2012.

